parameters: \C[27][Rade]\C[0] What's the matter? It's so noisy.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Regnus Grahardt was here, wasn't he?
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Why didn't you call for me?

Servant: Lord Regnus Grahardt said he had no business with Lady
Rade...
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Luca, what did he come for?
Servant: He came to entrust this to me to help Luna...
Servant: Lady Rade, I will deliver this to Luna. Please allow me.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Whatever happens to that girl is none of our concern.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Luca, hand it over to me.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] That girl and this country have nothing to do with me.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Luca, you've been acting strange ever since you met that girl. Just
leave it be. The farce is over.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] More importantly, where did Regnus Grahardt go?

Servant: Lady Rade, just as you pursue Regnus Grahardt, Luna pursues a
bright future for Jupiterino.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Don't compare me with that girl. Her wishes are trivial.

Servant: No... Lady Rade, if it has come to this, I must speak my
mind. Your desires are the trivial ones.

Servant: The only reason you chase after Regnus Grahardt is to
overcome your fear.

Servant: Years ago, you fought Regnus Grahardt and it ended in a draw,
but it greatly wounded your pride and instilled fear in you. You are
chasing him to overcome that fear.

Servant: I understand everything. You are not fixated on fighting
Regnus Grahardt. You just want to meet him to conquer your fear.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Is that all you wanted to say?

Servant: Luna is trying to save the suffering people of Jupiterino.
That's different from your selfish desires.

Servant: I will deliver this to Luna-san, even if it means quitting as
your servant.

Servant: Or will you kill me? That would be fine too. With your power,
it would be over in an instant.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] What value does that girl have?
Servant: She has value to me, even if not to you.
Servant: Lady Rade, I apologize... for defying you.

Servant: I will return after I have delivered this to Luna-san.
Farewell...
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Ughhhnnn! It's so frustrating! He really left! Bitten by my own dog!
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] That Luca...! When he comes back... I'm going to smack him so much!
